These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, horror, musical, martial-arts
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
2. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person watching musical movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | horror | martial-arts | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, roller, jet-ski, scooter
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the person driving the trike##7
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the scooter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | scooter | jet-ski | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
