1. the mechanic is on the left of the coach##1
2. the engineer is somewhere between the accountant and the coach##7
3. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | mechanic | coach | engineer | accountant |

