.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, fish, frog
1. the owner of the frog is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
3. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet   | fish | cat | frog | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
House: cape-cod, tower, ranch-style, wooden
1. the wooden house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the tower house is between the cape-cod house and the wooden house##2
3. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
4. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the wooden house##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| House   | ranch-style | cape-cod | tower | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, chess, poker, billiard
1. the person playing backgammon is somewhere between the person playing billiard and the person playing chess##7
2. the person playing poker is somewhere between the person playing backgammon and the person playing billiard##7
3. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Game   | billiard | poker | backgammon | chess |

