.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, march, december, october
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in december##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Birthday   | december | may | october | march |

